OL,3,CLife changing jaw joint surgery
OL,4,Cinspires woman to campaign for others
OL,6,FA woman who says her life has been
OL,7,Ftransformed by pioneering surgery is
OL,8,Fnow campaigning to help others living
OL,9,Fin constant pain.
OL,11,FLauren Bolton, from Rossendale in
OL,12,FLancashire, was in constant pain and
OL,13,Funable to eat solid foods, due to a
OL,14,F'locked-jaw' condition which gave her
OL,15,Fconstant pain.
