OL,3,CLife changing jaw joint surgery
OL,4,Cinspires woman to campaign for others
OL,6,FThe 31-year-old travelled to London at
OL,7,Fthe end of October 2025 to undergo
OL,8,Fprivate surgery to remove the damaged
OL,9,Fparts of the jaw joint, before
OL,10,Fsurgeons then replaced it with
OL,11,Ftitanium components to form a new one.
OL,13,FSince sharing her story, dozens of
OL,14,Fothers have been in touch with her
OL,15,Fdescribing similar situations, and she
OL,16,Fsays she is now determined to help
OL,17,Fthem.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
