OL,3,CLife changing jaw joint surgery
OL,4,Cinspires woman to campaign for others
OL,6,F"People aren't getting a detailed and
OL,7,Fprecise diagnosis a lot of the time
OL,8,Funtil years and years down the line,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,F"It was a good 10 years before I got
OL,12,Fan MRI scan - and that was because I
OL,13,Fbegged for one."
OL,15,FLauren travelled to London seven weeks
OL,16,Fafter surgery for her post-op
OL,17,Fappointment.
