OL,4,Cinspires woman to campaign for others
OL,6,FSpeaking after the appointment Deepak
OL,7,FKomath said: "I am delighted today,
OL,8,Fshe's made such good progress. It's
OL,9,Fbetter than what she's ever been, and
OL,10,Fwe can get even better, it's still
OL,11,Fvery early days.
OL,13,F"So she's got to do some physiotherapy
OL,14,Fto get back to normal, but she will be
OL,15,Fback to her happy self."
OL,17,FHer surgeon is only one of a handful
OL,18,Fin the country who can do jaw joint
OL,19,Freplacements.
