OL,6,FMr Komath said he has a long waiting
OL,7,Flist of patients, and agrees more
OL,8,Fspecialists are required to tackle the
OL,9,Fproblem.
OL,11,F"There are reasons for it, but the NHS
OL,12,Fis getting there," he said.
OL,14,F"We are training NHS surgeons and
OL,15,Fthings will get better... but we can't
OL,16,Fpossibly scan all of them."
