OL,4,Cinspires woman to campaign for others
OL,6,FSince her surgery, which was funded in
OL,7,Fpart by the generosity of Granada
OL,8,FReports viewers, Lauren has been able
OL,9,Fto eat a variety of foods, and says
OL,10,Fshe is looking forward to Christmas.
OL,12,F"(I) can't wait - Yorkshire puddings,
OL,13,Fpigs in blankets - I'm actually going
OL,14,Faway with my partner on Christmas day
OL,15,Ffor a couple of nights as well - and
OL,16,Fthere will be all the snacks you can
OL,17,Fthink of!" Lauren said.
OL,19,FHowever, her focus remains on raising
OL,20,Fawareness of painful conditions, and
OL,21,Fearly diagnosis.
