OL,4,Cinspires woman to campaign for others
OL,6,FShe said: "I had this whole career as
OL,7,Fa psychologist planned out, and it's
OL,8,Fjust been completely taken away
OL,9,Fbecause my whole life has been this -
OL,10,Fhospital appointments and fighting -
OL,11,Fand I look now in my thirties and I
OL,12,Fhaven't been able to do any of that.
OL,14,F"These health professionals that you
OL,15,Fgo and see where they're not doing the
OL,16,Fscans - this is the impact they're
OL,17,Fhaving on people's lives - it's not
OL,18,Fjust the pain, although that's awful -
OL,19,Fit's everything it touches."
